	(text "Generate 3.3V for the IOREF pin.\nThis only powers the level shifters, so LDO is fine here.\nThis is only needed because we can split the PCB and the\ndata connector only carries 5V. If you build a more integrated PCB\nuse the 3.3V from the core instead.\n"
